### Contact points

Its use for config where we want alert i use Gmail for this
For using Email or even outlook you need APP PASSWORD for configration
Afer save % test

### Alert rules
Setup alert rule, I setup rule for Nginx- When nginx goes down it will alert me on my gmail,

(
  probe_success{job="nginx-blackbox-external"} == 1
)
OR
on() vector(0)

### Alert condition
WHEN QUERY

Is below
1


### When Nginx went 0 it will alert me that nginx is down and when it's 1 it means Nginx is working fine
